1.x.x, 2010-11-xx:
 + Notifier#default_options;
 + local cache;
 + severity (level) threshold;
 + partial compatibility with Ruby Logger and other loggers:
   - Notifier#fatal { "Argument 'foo' not given." }
   - Notifier#error "Argument #{ @foo } mismatch."
   - Notifier#close

1.0.0, 2010-11-10:
 + initial stable version;
 * deprecated Gelf class is still there.
